  <brief_title>Exercise Versus Cognitive Behavioural Therapy on Cancer-related Fatigue</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of a Brief Endurance Exercise Program and of a Cognitive Behavioural Therapy on Patients With Cancer-related Fatigue</official_title>
  <sponsors>
