  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators compare the effects of two interventions, an endurance exercise program and
      a cognitive behavioural therapy, on the fatigue, quality of life, mood and physical
      performance of patients with a cancer-related fatigue syndrome. The intervention will be
      carried out for 4 weeks. Tests will be carried out at the beginning and at the end of the
      study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
